---
const links = [
  { href: 'https://github.com/fedidevkr/join-fediverse', label: 'GitHub' },
  { href: 'https://github.com/fedidevkr/join-fediverse/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md', label: '기여하기' },
  { href: 'https://github.com/fedidevkr/join-fediverse/blob/main/LICENSE', label: '라이선스' },
];
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-main">
    <div class="footer-brand">joinfediverse.kr</div>
    <p class="footer-copy">
      큰 플랫폼의 속도에서 한 걸음 벗어나, 더 잘 맞는 공동체를 찾기 위한 안내서.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-side">
    <ul class="footer-links">
      {links.map((link) => (
        <li><a href={link.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{link.label}</a></li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <div class="footer-meta">CC0 · 누구나 자유롭게 수정하고 공유할 수 있습니다.</div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    width: min(var(--section-width), calc(100vw - 2.5rem));
    margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.6rem 1.8rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(255, 251, 245, 0.7);
    border: 1px solid rgba(88, 69, 45, 0.12);
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .footer-main {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  .footer-copy,
  .footer-meta {
    color: var(--text-soft);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .footer-copy {
    margin-top: 0.55rem;
  }

  .footer-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.8rem 1.25rem;
    justify-content: end;
  }

  .footer-side {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: end;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    min-height: 44px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-soft);
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--sage);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .site-footer {
      width: min(var(--section-width), calc(100vw - 2rem));
      padding: 1.4rem 1.4rem;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .footer-side,
    .footer-links {
      justify-content: start;
      justify-items: start;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .site-footer {
      width: min(var(--section-width), calc(100vw - 1.25rem));
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1.6rem 1.25rem;
      gap: 1.4rem;
    }

    .footer-brand {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
    }
  }
</style>
